<!-- 
v5.5.1 comments

Make sure not to have more than 1 pair of <FTL></FTL> tags in hyperspace.xml.append, and most files. 
They contain everything but the xml encoding line, that's the norm. (BUT blueprints.xml in MV folder is different!)

REF for findLike and findName from "Bag Of Dumb (Fixed)"'s hyperspace.xml.append:
<mod:findLike type="crew">
	<mod:findName type = "race" name = "gnome">
		<mod:findLike type = "passiveStatBoosts">
			<mod:findName type = "statBoost" name = "silenced">
				<mod:findLike type = "blackList">
					<mod-append:box_damaged/>
					<mod-append:box_black_engaged/>
					<mod-append:box_white_engaged/>
				</mod:findLike>
			</mod:findName>
		</mod:findLike>
	</mod:findName>
</mod:findLike>

v5.5.1 comments End. -->

<!-- Modify global settings to allow MULTI-BATTLES (at the same beacon). 
Alas, happens to make S1 Leah stronger vs shieldless by replacing her drone by a beam drone.
Hopefully it lets us replace the enemy/neutral ship by another without killing it first,
since we can't reproduce the full effect of Console "EVENT". -->
<multiShipFix enabled="true"/>

